    public class AmpActivityFormFeature
extends AmpFeaturePanel<AmpActivityVersion>
    Main component hub for all activity form subcomponents. This is AmpFeaturePanel, as such, it supports OnePagerUtil.cascadeFmEnabled(AjaxRequestTarget, boolean, org.apache.wicket.Component) and OnePagerUtil.cascadeFmVisible(AjaxRequestTarget, boolean, org.apache.wicket.Component)

    Jun 7, 2011
